Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.67,0:01:49.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相遇是有各种各样的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.97,0:01:51.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果有只为战斗而相遇的话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.17,0:01:54.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些家伙不是红世之徒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.27,0:01:56.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放过他们没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.27,0:01:59.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可不是放过他们哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.77,0:02:01.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是被放过了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.47,0:02:04.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴  笨蛋马尔克
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.42,0:02:10.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通过电话交谈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.37,0:02:12.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,异世界的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.67,0:02:13.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和平的主妇
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.37,0:02:15.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也有这样的相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.97,0:02:22.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且女孩子可是比外观看起来早熟很多的哟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.17,0:02:25.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.07,0:02:28.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和夏娜的相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.97,0:02:30.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,究竟有什么意义呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.47,0:02:32.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,答案
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.07,0:02:34.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还遥不可知
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.77,0:02:42.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不和你做
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.72,0:03:17.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用担心也没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.72,0:03:19.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是和平井同学关系比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.52,0:03:20.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有恋爱感情啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.42,0:03:23.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.72,0:03:24.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是会介意的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.92,0:03:28.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜欢坂井同学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.62,0:03:33.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小缘也应该喜欢坂井同学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.92,0:03:36.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那坂井同学他…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.82,0:03:45.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不行啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.62,0:03:56.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然有点早
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.12,0:03:58.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们去散步吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.42,0:03:59.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾卡特琳娜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.82,0:04:12.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏…夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.22,0:04:16.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跑得稍微慢点呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.12,0:04:19.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,锻炼之后再这样身体可吃不消
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.62,0:04:20.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了啦  快爬上来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.32,0:04:25.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说是有东西想让我看才跟来的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.32,0:04:28.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.72,0:04:41.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来…还有这样的..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.42,0:04:41.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.72,0:04:44.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最喜欢的景色
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.62,0:05:01.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  等一下啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.92,0:05:14.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坂井那家伙还真悠哉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.62,0:05:17.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不知道他明不明白吉田同学的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.42,0:05:21.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又老实  又专一  又坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.72,0:05:24.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底对那么好的女孩有什么不满啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.22,0:05:35.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.22,0:05:39.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早…早上好  池同学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.32,0:05:41.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天也好早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.02,0:05:42.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉田同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.32,0:05:45.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今…今天起得特别早
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.72,0:05:47.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有点睡眠不足
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.92,0:05:50.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带狗散步到了河堤那…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.82,0:05:53.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后…然后…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.22,0:06:07.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.32,0:06:15.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我八音盒的钥匙？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.32,0:06:15.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.12,0:06:19.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为继续让哥哥这么等下去实在于心不忍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.22,0:06:21.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去持有者那里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.92,0:06:24.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不得到贽殿遮那的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.72,0:06:25.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.22,0:06:28.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说昨天并没有出手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.62,0:06:32.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可我却不认为那个悼词朗诵者会这么乖乖退却
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.42,0:06:33.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想就算是你们俩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.72,0:06:37.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要同时对付两个火雾战士也不是那么轻松的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.22,0:06:40.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,委托人都说没关系了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.42,0:06:42.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就请你老实服从命令吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.92,0:06:46.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你应该知道火雾战士是不会共同行动的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.62,0:06:50.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种虾兵蟹将就算万一冲着我们来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.22,0:06:51.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,顺手解决掉便行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.52,0:06:53.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.32,0:06:54.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.52,0:06:59.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小瞧她的话不管从何种方面来说都是很危险的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.62,0:07:00.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小瞧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.82,0:07:04.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在着摇篮庭院里可是无敌的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.52,0:07:07.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正因为如此才希望你保护好八音盒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.32,0:07:09.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这命令是否真那么奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.02,0:07:11.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.02,0:07:13.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请说实话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.32,0:07:18.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说被那红世之徒放过是骗人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.42,0:07:21.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是因为我们是累赘所以才没战斗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.62,0:07:23.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我们的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.52,0:07:25.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大姐给当成虾兵蟹将的话可无法忍受
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.22,0:07:28.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了  说些什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.92,0:07:29.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.72,0:07:37.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在屋顶吃也挺新鲜的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.22,0:07:38.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.62,0:07:42.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实今天清晨那会…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.92,0:07:45.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么也睡不着
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.92,0:07:48.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是在河堤那散了会步
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.82,0:07:51.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后在堤坝上看见了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.62,0:07:53.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,池同学
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.82,0:07:55.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说过吧  什么也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.12,0:08:00.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太奇怪了  像这样把吉田同学的好意不管不顾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.22,0:08:02.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.92,0:08:04.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.52,0:08:07.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就可以了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.22,0:08:09.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做这种半吊子的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.12,0:08:11.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后伤心的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.92,0:08:12.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要说了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.92,0:08:17.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没拜托你这种事啊…池同学
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.42,0:08:19.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉田同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.72,0:08:25.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没这意思…不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.62,0:08:45.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今早看见你们的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.92,0:08:47.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实不是我而是吉田同学
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.62,0:08:49.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.22,0:08:52.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后早上就听说了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.62,0:08:54.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己也不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.52,0:08:57.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看着你像往常一样吃着吉田同学的便当时
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.62,0:08:58.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不由的就…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.72,0:09:01.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但看来是多管闲事了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.32,0:09:04.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本不打算这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.42,0:09:07.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也会失败呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.02,0:09:08.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失败？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.12,0:09:12.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是啊  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.62,0:09:13.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.92,0:09:16.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被你指责的话虽然很丢人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.62,0:09:17.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却没有错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.22,0:09:20.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但光是我说的话先别管
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.92,0:09:22.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说…自己正在反省啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.42,0:09:31.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,问你件事行么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.32,0:09:36.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…对吉田同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.77,0:09:39.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.27,0:10:03.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.47,0:10:05.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.67,0:10:09.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,池同学完全没有错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.17,0:10:13.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可我却因为自己说不出口的话被那么干脆地说了出来就…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.07,0:10:15.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是却很怕说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.67,0:10:18.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,觉得就保持这样好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.77,0:10:21.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坂井同学和小缘
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.47,0:10:23.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是在一起而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.57,0:10:25.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来却像是紧紧连结在一起的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.97,0:10:30.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果想硬挤进去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.37,0:10:36.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在的我和坂井同学间\N微小羁绊的关系可能会破裂也说不定
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.47,0:10:42.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.67,0:10:44.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.97,0:10:55.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小缘太狡猾了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.77,0:10:57.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,指什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.27,0:11:01.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小缘也喜欢坂井同学吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.27,0:11:03.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.27,0:11:04.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我对悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.07,0:11:08.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但却毫不领情  装作不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.17,0:11:11.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但却比我更加更加的接近
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.77,0:11:12.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太狡猾了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.57,0:11:14.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系的！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.87,0:11:16.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小缘不也是在逃避吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.67,0:11:20.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么一定要被你说这种话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.47,0:11:21.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有说了才会改变
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.47,0:11:25.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我也喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.47,0:11:31.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我也喜欢坂井同学
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.97,0:11:38.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠二是…悠二是我的…我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.07,0:11:40.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.57,0:11:45.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我确实像小缘说的在逃避也不一定
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.57,0:11:49.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是已经不同了…已经决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.67,0:11:51.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不再含糊不清
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.87,0:11:55.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不靠别人  自己努力试试
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.97,0:11:59.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小缘对坂井同学说过喜欢他么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.17,0:12:04.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会好好对他说的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.77,0:12:05.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.47,0:12:07.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,清楚地用自己的嘴说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.47,0:12:07.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.17,0:12:10.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说  坂井同学  我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.87,0:12:11.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.87,0:12:13.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.57,0:12:14.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  要说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.57,0:12:16.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让坂井同学来决定
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.37,0:12:20.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会输给没说过喜欢他的小缘的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.67,0:12:24.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也…我也对悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.57,0:12:33.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这难道是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.27,0:12:34.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自在法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.07,0:12:40.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.57,0:12:43.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干嘛碍事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.87,0:12:49.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上让你听听我的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.17,0:12:51.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠二和我拥有的远比你多的多
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.37,0:12:54.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝不会输给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.07,0:12:55.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.67,0:12:57.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会输
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.77,0:13:03.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  泰莉亚露
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.67,0:13:05.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.97,0:13:08.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那边有贽殿遮那
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.77,0:13:10.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.67,0:13:13.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就尽快去拿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.87,0:13:23.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「爱染」的…是昨天那些家伙干的好事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.67,0:13:25.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干的还真是大手笔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.57,0:13:29.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备如何啊  我美丽的酒杯——玛裘莉·顿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.77,0:13:31.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再让他们放一马？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.07,0:13:32.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.47,0:13:36.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正他们的目标也不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.77,0:13:38.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不用勉强出头
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.57,0:13:39.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.77,0:13:40.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.07,0:13:42.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用那么消极吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.17,0:13:45.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会尽量不拖后腿的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.57,0:13:47.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请去战斗吧  大姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.47,0:13:50.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,够了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.07,0:13:53.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛裘莉小姐不去的话  我去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.37,0:13:56.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起给当成累赘来要好多了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.77,0:13:58.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.47,0:13:59.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大姐  我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.37,0:14:01.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会打场漂亮的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.77,0:14:02.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请看好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.47,0:14:05.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  真是的  知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.97,0:14:08.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之  先去以前那栋百货大厦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.97,0:14:11.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恋物癖混蛋的遗物说不定还能派点用场
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.87,0:14:12.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.77,0:14:14.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是封绝吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.07,0:14:15.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.07,0:14:19.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但不明白为什么张那么大
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.67,0:14:21.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说可能是陷阱？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.37,0:14:24.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,红世之徒的气息有三个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.27,0:14:27.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朝这边来的有两个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.17,0:14:29.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不动的只有一个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.47,0:14:30.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三对一
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.97,0:14:32.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挺麻烦的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.27,0:14:32.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说  夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.37,0:14:36.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人  去向玛裘莉小姐求助怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.67,0:14:38.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在游泳池见过了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.47,0:14:40.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在的悼词朗诵者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.27,0:14:41.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能成为战力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.67,0:14:42.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起等着攻过来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.77,0:14:44.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该先打过去比较好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.10,0:14:46.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.77,0:14:49.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠二  你找个地方躲起来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.27,0:14:49.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.77,0:14:52.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下  我也要去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.97,0:14:54.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是很危险的战斗哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.87,0:14:55.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.17,0:14:59.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果受到避火戒指无法防御的攻击的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.97,0:15:01.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一瞬间就会消失
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.17,0:15:03.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有参战的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.97,0:15:06.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且也没有一起来的必要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.27,0:15:08.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.67,0:15:10.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是有点很在意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.47,0:15:14.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,维持这类似封绝的自在法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.97,0:15:18.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,需要目前所感觉得到的更为大量的存在之力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.57,0:15:20.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白意思吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.07,0:15:25.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫非有着为此而设的机关吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.67,0:15:28.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是宝具还是自在法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.87,0:15:30.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许是其他的什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.87,0:15:32.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要找到这个就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.37,0:15:33.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别慌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.57,0:15:35.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能那么简单就找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.87,0:15:39.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且整个城市都在对手的掌握之中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.67,0:15:42.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知何时会有红世之徒或磷子袭击过来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.27,0:15:44.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,红世之徒或磷子…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.97,0:15:46.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.77,0:15:51.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会尽力做自己能做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.27,0:15:58.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜  万一派上什么用场的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.47,0:15:59.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我点奖励吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.97,0:16:00.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奖励？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.17,0:16:06.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了  吵死了  吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.47,0:16:07.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.47,0:16:08.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那  待会见
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.47,0:16:11.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.57,0:16:13.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.87,0:16:27.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看啊看啊  泰莉亚露
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.57,0:16:31.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是贽殿遮那  贽殿遮那在那啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.87,0:16:34.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  是啊  哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.57,0:16:36.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请再稍微等一下呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.57,0:16:38.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初次见面
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.17,0:16:42.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这位就是我的哥哥「爱染自」——索拉特
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.07,0:16:44.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是「爱染他」——泰莉亚露
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.27,0:16:47.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知你是哪位的契约者呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.27,0:16:51.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是「天壤劫火」——亚拉斯托尔的火雾战士
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.07,0:16:54.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「炎发灼眼的讨伐者」——夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.27,0:16:57.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天壤？好老的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.97,0:17:00.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这种事怎么都好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.27,0:17:04.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和你只不过是顺便玩一下而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.07,0:17:05.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,顺便？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.97,0:17:07.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛…这些家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.57,0:17:10.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,粘在一起好恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.17,0:17:13.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事情也很简单
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.37,0:17:16.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我哥哥想要你那把剑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.37,0:17:18.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.57,0:17:21.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,耳朵不好？还是脑袋？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.47,0:17:22.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我再说一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.27,0:17:24.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把这剑…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.07,0:17:24.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没必要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.57,0:17:29.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贽殿遮那
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.67,0:17:45.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼哼  哥哥的「吸血鬼」的滋味如何
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.67,0:17:50.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs20}吸血鬼:「爱染自」索拉特所持有的剑型宝具  拥有注入存在之力后能使接触者受到伤害的特殊能力  并可以任意选择受伤处
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.77,0:17:50.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只需要注入存在之力便可将接触剑的对手任意受伤哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.57,0:17:53.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.67,0:17:55.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要随便突击
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.37,0:17:58.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贽殿遮那  想要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.37,0:18:02.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下  贽殿遮那
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.27,0:18:07.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是现在把大家静止住的叫自在法的东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.27,0:18:08.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.07,0:18:10.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那变态兄妹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.47,0:18:11.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然趁我们没注意的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.87,0:18:14.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,设下了那么大的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.57,0:18:16.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在情况如何
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.47,0:18:20.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天遇见的红世之徒  其中两个正在和小鬼战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.97,0:18:22.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另一个则在城外
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.47,0:18:24.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么时候去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.77,0:18:25.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.87,0:18:26.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是说了么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.97,0:18:29.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目标又不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.37,0:18:32.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛裘莉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.07,0:18:33.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.37,0:18:35.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有个火炬在动
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.97,0:18:37.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.17,0:18:48.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会那么想派上用场
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.67,0:18:49.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都这么害怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.27,0:18:53.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直躲在这里的话就安全了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.77,0:18:55.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.57,0:18:59.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想派上用场的话  就只有去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.07,0:19:01.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望什么都别出来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.47,0:19:10.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有两下子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.67,0:19:11.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战力估计错误了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.67,0:19:14.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贽殿遮那
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.87,0:19:16.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.47,0:19:25.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还真是不错的景色
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.77,0:19:30.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.17,0:19:35.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,红…红世之徒？磷子？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.37,0:19:40.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  去拿贽殿遮那吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.57,0:19:41.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.27,0:19:47.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贽殿遮那
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.17,0:19:50.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我的  是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.77,0:19:53.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我的  是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.47,0:19:57.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是现在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.17,0:20:11.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.87,0:20:14.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.27,0:20:17.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.57,0:20:19.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是贽殿遮那的力量吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.17,0:20:21.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炎之剑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.47,0:20:27.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能  再生的太快了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.57,0:20:29.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了  亚拉斯托尔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.27,0:20:36.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这大得愚蠢的封绝本身\N正是供给他们存在之力的像工厂一样的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.97,0:20:37.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.87,0:20:42.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有那么大的破坏力和刚才的再生就能说明这一点了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.67,0:20:46.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,问题在于力量的供给源在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.37,0:20:48.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.67,0:20:51.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然让我的哥哥受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.67,0:20:55.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不仅如此  竟然还踩我哥哥的脸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.37,0:20:58.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  可怜的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.07,0:21:00.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定很疼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.67,0:21:02.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很厉害哦  泰莉亚露
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.37,0:21:04.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贽殿遮那果然很厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.27,0:21:08.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剑就暂时忍耐下先用这把吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.47,0:21:10.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个马上就能到手了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.87,0:21:11.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.97,0:21:15.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起这个  如果我的感觉正确的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.17,0:21:16.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,力量的源头是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.27,0:21:18.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要上咯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.07,0:21:25.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白费力气
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.97,0:21:27.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打算去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.27,0:21:34.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了  他们的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.77,0:21:36.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所保护的东西是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.17,0:21:36.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.27,0:21:48.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火雾战士
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.67,0:21:50.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一瞬间就好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.97,0:21:51.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要一口气
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.97,0:21:54.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用一击必杀的…力量
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.68,0:21:59.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燃烧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.57,0:22:15.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.07,0:24:28.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一心只想要贽殿遮那的索拉特
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.97,0:24:31.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切只献给哥哥的泰莉亚露
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.97,0:24:33.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,互相拥抱的「爱染」兄妹的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.27,0:24:35.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜所看到的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.27,0:24:39.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,次回  校舍后的宣战通告
